<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
      h1 { color: #1F2937; border-bottom: 2px solid #059669; padding-bottom: 10px; }
      h2 { color: #374151; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px; }
      .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
      .terms-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0; }
      .terms-table td { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
      .terms-table td:first-child { font-weight: bold; width: 40%; }
      .highlight { background-color: #F0FDF4; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #059669; margin: 15px 0; }
      .signature-line { margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #333; width: 200px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Equity Partner Mortgage Agreement</h1>
      <p>Loan Agreement Contract</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Loan Details</h2>
      <table class="terms-table">
        <tr>
          <td>Property Address</td>
          <td><%= @application.property_address %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Property Value</td>
          <td>$<%= number_with_precision(@application.property_value, precision: 0, delimiter: ',') %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Loan Amount</td>
          <td>$<%= number_with_precision(@application.loan_amount, precision: 0, delimiter: ',') %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Loan-to-Value (LTV)</td>
          <td><%= number_with_precision(@application.ltv_ratio * 100, precision: 1) %>%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Interest Rate (Annual)</td>
          <td><%= number_with_precision(@application.interest_rate * 100, precision: 2) %>%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Loan Term</td>
          <td><%= @application.loan_term_years %> years</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Monthly Income Payment</td>
          <td>$<%= number_with_precision(@application.monthly_payment, precision: 2, delimiter: ',') %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <div class="highlight">
        <p><strong>You Own Your Property:</strong> You retain full ownership of your property. This is a mortgage, not a sale or equity release.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Monthly Guaranteed Income:</strong> You receive guaranteed monthly income from your loan proceeds being invested. This is not a loan you must repay.</p>
        
        <p><strong>No Monthly Repayments:</strong> You do not make monthly mortgage payments. Your income is guaranteed regardless of investment performance.</p>
        
        <p><strong>No Negative Equity Guarantee (NNEG):</strong> You are protected by a guarantee that ensures you will never owe more than your property is worth when the loan is settled.</p>
        
        <p><strong>When Loan is Repaid:</strong> The loan is repaid from the proceeds of your property sale or from your estate. You (or your heirs) keep any equity that remains after the loan is settled.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Monthly Income Payment Schedule</h2>
      <p>Your guaranteed monthly income of <strong>$<%= number_with_precision(@application.monthly_payment, precision: 2, delimiter: ',') %></strong> will be paid on the <strong>15th of each month</strong> into your nominated bank account.</p>
      
      <p>Income payments will continue for the duration of the loan term or until the loan is settled, whichever is sooner.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Your Rights and Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You must notify us of any changes to your contact information</li>
        <li>You must maintain the property in reasonable condition</li>
        <li>You must maintain appropriate property insurance</li>
        <li>You may not sell the property without settling the loan</li>
        <li>You will receive quarterly statements showing your account balance and income received</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Borrower Acknowledgement</h2>
      <p>I acknowledge that I have read, understood, and agree to the terms and conditions of this Equity Partner Mortgage Agreement. I understand that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>I own the property and will receive guaranteed monthly income</li>
        <li>I will not make monthly loan repayments</li>
        <li>The loan will be repaid when my property is sold or from my estate</li>
        <li>I am protected by the No Negative Equity Guarantee</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-line" style="margin-top: 40px;"></div>
    <p style="margin-top: 5px;">Borrower Signature</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280;">
      <strong>Date Generated:</strong> <%= Time.current.strftime('%d %B %Y') %><br>
      <strong>Agreement ID:</strong> <%= @application.id %><br>
      This is a certified agreement. Keep this document for your records.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
